21#include "mpc-impl.h"
22
23/* the rounding mode is mpfr_rnd_t here since we return an mpfr number */
24int
25mpc_abs (mpfr_ptr a, mpc_srcptr b, mpfr_rnd_t rnd)
26{
27 return mpfr_hypot (a, mpc_realref(b), mpc_imagref(b), rnd);
28}
